  "detailed_description": "The Traykonians don't believe there's intelligent life on Earth, and it's up to you to prove them wrong.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nManipulate gravity to solve over 60 of their mind-bending puzzles... just try not to accidentally fling yourself into any lasers.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nGraviton is a challenging puzzle game in the same vein as Baba is You and Portal. Do you have what it takes to beat it?",
